00:51:53.120 --> 00:52:09.810
ben: There are two lines of work, for the past month that I was looking into. The first one was looking into how guest programs use memory, and we've observed, then, on some fixtures on EAST,

358
00:52:09.830 --> 00:52:14.530
ben: Some of them were crushing, and this was not due to logic reasons, but…

359
00:52:14.610 --> 00:52:21.610
